QueryText: how to prepare tobacco decoction , neam oil garlic emulsion , fertilizer recommendation for banana

Tobacco decoction
soak 100 g tobacco in 1 liter water and kept it over night.after that strain it and make it a solution then . mix 20 g barsoap in 100 ml water and mix them together After that  dilute this solution with 5 liter water 
Neam oil garlic emulsion
     Take 20 g garlic and make it as a paste and mix it with 50 ml watwr and  then extract it .then take 5g bar soap and dilute it with 50 ml water .and mix the both solutions with 900 ml water and mix it well after that add 20 mi castor oil and and stir it well.
